message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CC". This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for generating question-answer hierarchies, which are relevant to several sub-fields of computer science such as computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
